title: Always post adding fragments
message:
Always post adding fragments

Prevents issues when adding fragments before properly removing them from their former container.
This approach now allows less wary fragment removal/adding, so we can remove fragments directly before re-adding them.
Before, when selecting remove/sort, fragments where removed immediately and had to be re-added on cancel, now nothing is done until OK is pressed.
